snippet.title: Quest Givers
snippet.description:
Go and get hooked on http://www.questgivers.com
Writing Dungeons and Dragons adventures and adventures for other tabletop role-playing games requires a lot of quest ideas and stories. This YouTube channel presents modules, one shots, adventures and ideas to build your adventure path or follow the campaign with your tabletop role-playing game group.
